  "detailed_description": "<strong>——你将向整个太阳系证明。<br><br>——钢铁是怎样炼成的。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400590/extras/2f287eda6725053049a4d3d46ec6693d.avif?t=1707125451\" width=614 height=198 /></span><br>《彗星战团》是一款机战题材的视觉小说。<br>玩家将跟随佣兵·柯伊伯白狼的视角，在战火中登上有着流星旗帜美誉的机体，卷入风起云涌的时代浪潮之中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400590/extras/4e29b1d4347b2f3e736d12821c192973.avif?t=1707125451\" width=615 height=199 /></span><br>西元26世纪的太阳系，冥王星等外环行星沦为巨型军工企业的殖民地。<br>与妹妹相依为命的违法佣兵柯伊伯白狼，被迫接下刺杀亚罗拉夫·春明集团大使的委托。<br>但谁也没有想到，白狼与集团大使的相遇，将揭开又一次旗帜战争的帷幕。<br><strong>“你不是白狼，你究竟是谁？”</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400590/extras/614ae721c3e46d03990d135b9100a8f5.avif?t=1707125451\" width=615 height=199 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400590/extras/3d55a6439a515888896e89f86e74dbf3.avif?t=1707125451\" width=614 height=198 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400590/extras/1cf5bae30721b0ad032a60663c299fe7.avif?t=1707125451\" width=614 height=198 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400590/extras/7d56e372d7dca22a7e0b4c85e37197d4.avif?t=1707125451\" width=614 height=198 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2400590/extras/87501e169b5ebcc1348a8d30ba88a52f.avif?t=1707125451\" width=615 height=199 /></span><br>·本作文本量为10万字，剧本反复雕琢，语言简洁凝练<br>·风格化的美术，二十余名角色，共同呈现独特的科幻战争世界<br>·十余首原创音乐搭配全角色配音，营造身临其境的机甲战争感受<br>·全剧情采用高速运镜特殊演出展现，营造影视化的视听观感<br><br>《彗星战团》是本工作室的首款游戏，隶属于跨平台跨玩法的旗帜战争三部曲，剧情可独立完整体验。本团队专注于开发机战题材游戏，致力分享机战作品的独特魅力。<br><br>==联系我们==<br>B站：@彗星战团<br>微博：@彗星战团<br>Q群：829934222",
